<div class="content" name="LM_CHALLENGE" uuid="bb8eca90-41bc-4ca4-8419-defdf043e01b"><p>The <b>LM_CHALLENGE</b> structure carries a LAN Manager
authentication challenge.</p><dl>
<dd>
<div><pre> typedef struct {
   CHAR data[8];
 } LM_CHALLENGE;
</pre></div>
</dd></dl><p><b>data:</b> A string of eight characters that
contains a LAN Manager authentication challenge, which is an unencrypted <span><a href="b5e7d25a-40b2-41c8-9611-98f53358af66#gt_001c0e40-0980-417d-853c-f7cb34ba6d3b" data-linktype="relative-path">nonce</a></span>.</p><p>For more information, see <span><a href="https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=89929" data-linktype="external">[LANMAN]</a></span>.</p></div>